PrecisTransfer (a) to the SOLICITOR GENERAL OF CANADA of all the powers, duties and functions of the Minister of Employment and Immigration in relation to immigration, other than those relating to immigration policy, and (b) to the DEPARTMENT OF THE SOLICITOR GENERAL of the control and supervision of certain portions of the Public Service in the Canada Employment and Immigration Commission, more particularly: . 1. Immigration Policy - Politique d'immigration 2. Immigration Operations and - Opérations de l'immigration et les regional immigration opérations régionales de operations l'immigration 3. International Service - Service international 4. Business Immigration Branch - Direction générale de l'immigration des gens d'affaires 5. Immigration Secretariat - Secrétariat de l'Immigration .
